    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――千紗と沙季が出場した、ユニットバトル決勝前日",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "沙季、お疲れ様。最後の練習は終わったのか？",
      "startTime": 3.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、ついさっき終わったところです\n千紗は……サニピの皆さんと話してますね",
      "startTime": 12.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても……沙季も千紗も\nここ数日で一気に成長したな",
      "startTime": 19.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "顔つきから違うし、ユニットとしての完成度も抜群だ\n一体何をしたらここまで変われるんだ？",
      "startTime": 27.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "つい数日前までは、どうやったらこのユニットが\n良くなるのかずっと悩んでいたんですが……",
      "startTime": 33.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗に言われたんです\n「お姉ちゃんは本当は前に出たいんじゃないの？」って",
      "startTime": 40.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "その上、「このままお姉ちゃんが譲るなら、私の方が\n前に出て目立っちゃうんだから」とまで言われまして",
      "startTime": 49.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "驚いたな……千紗がそんな大胆なことを言ったのか",
      "startTime": 53.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "私も驚きましたし、千紗が独り立ちして遠くへ行って\nしまうような気がして寂しくもなりました",
      "startTime": 62.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "ですが……それ以上に千紗がこんなにはっきりと自分の\n気持ちを話してくれたことが嬉しくて",
      "startTime": 70.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "何より、私自身の……前に出たいという欲求に\n気付かせてくれて、感謝しているんです",
      "startTime": 78.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……姉妹揃って一皮むけた訳だな",
      "startTime": 82.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、そうですね。……あ、千紗\nそれでは、そろそろ帰りますね",
      "startTime": 91.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "明日の決勝、楽しみにしていて下さい\n必ず優勝しますから",
      "startTime": 99.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7166.666666699995,
          "startTime": 107.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "驚いたな、あそこまで言い切るなんて\nそれだけ自信があるということか……明日が楽しみだ",
      "startTime": 106.3666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12266.666666600002,
          "startTime": 118.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "皆さん、今日は私と千紗のパフォーマンスを\n見ていただき、本当にありがとうございます！",
      "startTime": 116.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "きっと、今まで皆さんが見たことのない\n私と千紗の姿を見せられたのではと思っています",
      "startTime": 123.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "……あら？　千紗ったら照れてるの？\n曲が終わったとたんにいつも通りね……ふふ",
      "startTime": 131.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9966.666666599991,
          "startTime": 141.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、改めて……皆さん、本当に\nありがとうございました！",
      "startTime": 140.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "二人で歌えて本当に良かった\nこれからも……ずっと一緒に頑張ろうね、千紗",
      "startTime": 146.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "凄い歓声だ……それだけ、二人のステージが\n素晴らしかったということだな",
      "startTime": 154.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（この後、二人は見事優勝を果たした）\n（しっかりと労ってお祝いしないとな）",
      "startTime": 161.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 165.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4466.666666599991,
          "startTime": 170.1333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4800.000000000011,
          "startTime": 170.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "沙季、お疲れ様。何してるんだ？",
      "startTime": 167.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です\nユニットバトルの感想を調べていました",
      "startTime": 174.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのライブでも私のことを書いてくれる方は\nいましたけど……今回はその数が凄く多いんです！",
      "startTime": 181.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "今までももちろん楽しかったんですが、千紗との\nユニットで前に出る楽しさや快感を知ってしまいました",
      "startTime": 189.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "それだけ手応えが掴めたのはいいことだな\n月ストの活動にもぜひ生かしてくれ",
      "startTime": 197.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　……はぁぁ～。決勝の舞台から見た\n観客の皆さんの熱狂する顔が忘れられません……",
      "startTime": 207.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "横を見れば、今までにないくらい自信に溢れた\n千紗と目が合って……嬉しくて胸が高鳴って……",
      "startTime": 216.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ええっと……沙季？　おーい……？",
      "startTime": 221.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！\n私、今までやったことがない仕事がしてみたいです！",
      "startTime": 227.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski021.m4a",
      "text": "決勝の後の打ち上げで千紗とも話してたんです\n「この勢いでいろんなチャレンジがしたいね」って！",
      "startTime": 236.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか。分かった、分かったから\n一旦落ち着いてくれ",
      "startTime": 243.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski022.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ！\nす、すみません、熱くなり過ぎました",
      "startTime": 246.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski023.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、チャレンジがしたいのは本当ですから\nよろしくお願いします",
      "startTime": 254.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "startTime": 257.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロにオファーがあった仕事から\nいくつか見繕ってみたよ",
      "startTime": 261.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski024.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか！？　ありがとうございます！",
      "startTime": 263.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "断りの連絡を入れようと思っていた仕事も\nいくつかまとめてみたんだ。見てもらえるか？",
      "startTime": 269.1333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5300.000000000011,
          "startTime": 274.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski025.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。一つ目はグラビアで……え？\n有名雑誌の表紙じゃないですか！　どうして断ろうと？",
      "startTime": 278.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "路線がなかなか過激なんだ。仕事としては大きいが\n星見のみんなのイメージに合わないと思ってな",
      "startTime": 287.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski026.m4a",
      "text": "やりたいです！　やらせて下さい！",
      "startTime": 290.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "え。い、いや、もうちょっとじっくり\n検討してくれていいんだぞ？",
      "startTime": 296.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski027.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です！　どんなところに\n私の魅力が眠っているのか分かりませんから！",
      "startTime": 301.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski028.m4a",
      "text": "今の私なら、多少過激な衣装であっても\n着こなすことが出来ると思います！",
      "startTime": 308.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "待て待て。……次のページに、ここ最近の表紙を\nまとめたから、それを見てから決めてくれ",
      "startTime": 314.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3300.0000000000114,
          "startTime": 318.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski029.m4a",
      "text": "……きゃあっ！？　は、肌の露出がこんなに……！？\nこ、これは、さすがに、ちょっと……",
      "startTime": 323.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "確認して良かっただろ？　これはお断りしておくよ\nそれで、次なんだが……こういうのはどうだろう？",
      "startTime": 331.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2933.3333333999576,
          "startTime": 334.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski030.m4a",
      "text": "あ、この番組……私も知ってます\n確か、バラエティの色が相当強いですよね？",
      "startTime": 341.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski031.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。出演出来るアイドルは、可愛いだけじゃなく\n笑いが取れることが条件……ですか",
      "startTime": 350.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski032.m4a",
      "text": "やります！　頑張って特訓しますから！",
      "startTime": 354.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　い、いや、正直……かなり厳しいと思うぞ？",
      "startTime": 358.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski033.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてですか！？　私だって、頑張ればきっと……！",
      "startTime": 363.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "鈴村さんやこころのように\n笑いを取れる自信はあるのか？",
      "startTime": 369.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski034.m4a",
      "text": "……ゆ、優ちゃんとこころちゃんのように……ですか？\nそれは、ちょっと……厳しいものが……",
      "startTime": 377.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh021.m4a",
      "text": "あの二人くらいの力がないと\nとんでもない事故に繋がりそうだから避けてたんだ",
      "startTime": 384.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski035.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうなんですね……分かりました\n準備していただいてすみませんが……やめておきます",
      "startTime": 393.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh022.m4a",
      "text": "（まさかここまで前のめりになるとは）\n（やる気があるのはいいことだが大丈夫だろうか……？）",
      "startTime": 401.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}